{"tid":1630802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飯民打手，求下你地唔好再叫人出港島儲人數………","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:15:17.000Z","uid":202464,"like":71,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5720ee2129c4f175333bc1fbf0c0d91ce42a9986","tid":1630802,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"你地食開人血饅頭我明，<br />\n<br />\n今次可唔可以高抬貴手，<br />\n<br />\n放過班年輕人啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n唔好再為左製造「二百萬人塞爆港島」畫面畀你地打飛機，而犧牲年輕人啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我當求下你地，<br />\n<br />\n你地都係為錢，我捐埋條底褲畀你啦"},{"pid":"da926a1fce7400f8280603d99d046a26b673ff16","tid":1630802,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"11d34200ef7315c13871076f0e4f59ad029d1870","tid":1630802,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f194988c5eb8c3e46cbc3c8f0e6c931a76de5dc","tid":1630802,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:47:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553a4f773cecf4eb718689a818ca12cd19bd4550","tid":1630802,"uid":12609,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:47:47.000Z","msg":"今時今日日真係唔適大遊行<br />\n只適個地區遊擊"},{"pid":"9f35ba362b8611eab46832cf5a21d2cbea8c25ec","tid":1630802,"uid":202464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:48:17.000Z","msg":"民陣既大佬，請高抬貴手。"},{"pid":"360d9f6d5602f6008e343d7d317719e0f4810