,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8854d39528cc76438d22678fe4ee42a72fe107","tid":1630802,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"要選行路返到屋企既路線"},{"pid":"1bb00473f094f422e14127b7ab02118bac2963c3","tid":1630802,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n分化"},{"pid":"2dbd6948ea73b78c31957eaf687351b80c48bef2","tid":1630802,"uid":178440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"今時今日人數仲有咩用，二百萬人遊行都不獲回應。揸下春袋仲實際"},{"pid":"8229174f8ff0cb7b7c71e3dbc9b7e3c4b5b6f441","tid":1630802,"uid":74302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:19.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n根本ON9<br />\n而家邊個同你計人數?<br />\n有人計咩自從818 之後???<br />\n分區開花有咩人計過人數呀又?<br />\n<br />\n仲叫人去港島儲人數，咪撚ON9啦<br />\n班狗都冇用毅進制去計人數啦, 少少人力都慳番啦<br />\n<br />\n真係為大家著想既，仲點會推我地去港島死呀?<br />\n你知唔知大家等巴士過海驚比人叫哂落車，坐船一落船成排狗拎住槍望你出來既感覺係點呀? 好撚好玩呀真係?"},{"pid":"7a2c787d67d4193419ab7ff4a24a1f8166cbc137","tid":1630802,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:30.000Z","msg":"民陣今次可唔可以食少一次人血饅頭？<br />\n<br />\n我求下你地啦。"},{"pid":"0f57f4849695f86b5801a70069fd214b23e2a3bf","tid":1630802,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"92b87b70d695b36a94b6b6e1b45237124bd75742","tid":1630802,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bb00473f094f422e14127b7ab02118bac2963c3","tid":1630802,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"請你為年輕人著想。<br />\n<br />\n做少一次打手啦。"},{"pid":"9c8b1e1914ccee3b08a9c8b59a8dbcba15f87e26","tid":1630802,"uid":93311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,